# Security Requirements

## MANDATORY Security Rules

- Validate ALL inputs
- Parameterized queries only (NO string concatenation)
- JWT/OAuth2 for auth
- Rate limiting on all endpoints
- HTTPS/TLS only
- Never hardcode secrets
- Security headers: CSP, HSTS, X-Frame-Options

